DERVISH DANCER			KEY:Bard Archetype ~ DERVISH DANCER				CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.BardArchetype.BardSuggestion.BardMassSuggestion.BardDirgeOfDoom.BardFrighteningPerformance.BardBardicKnowledge.BardLoreMaster.BardVersatilePerformance.BardSoothingPerformance.BardDeadlyPerformance	PRECLASS:1,Bard=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Bard Archetype ~ DERVISH DANCER],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.BardSuggestion,TYPE.BardMassSuggestion,TYPE.BardDirgeOfDoom,TYPE.BardFrighteningPerformance,TYPE.BardBardicKnowledge,TYPE.BardLoreMaster,TYPE.BardVersatilePerformance,TYPE.BardSoothingPerformance,TYPE.BardDeadlyPerformance]		DESC:Not all bards inspire others with their performances. Dervish dancers enter a near-mystical trance that allows them to push their bodies beyond normal limits.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.32	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon and Armor Proficiency ~ DERVISH DANCER|PRECLASS:1,Bard=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Battle Dance ~ DERVISH DANCER|PRECLASS:1,Bard=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Rain of Blows ~ DERVISH DANCER|PRECLASS:1,Bard=6	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Razor's Kiss ~ DERVISH DANCER|PRECLASS:1,Bard=8	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Leaf on the Wind ~ DERVISH DANCER|PRECLASS:1,Bard=14	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Fleet ~ DERVISH DANCER|PRECLASS:1,Bard=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Versatile Dance ~ DERVISH DANCER|PRECLASS:1,Bard=2	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dance of Fury ~ DERVISH DANCER|PRECLASS:1,Bard=12	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Battle Fury ~ DERVISH DANCER|PRECLASS:1,Bard=20
