Unarmed Fighter				KEY:Fighter Archetype ~ Unarmed Fighter		CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.FighterArchetype.FighterWeaponProficiencies.FighterArmorProficiencies.FighterBonusFeats.FighterBravery.FighterWeaponTraining_ALL.FighterArmorTraining_ALL.FighterArmorMastery.FighterWeaponMastery				PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1							PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Fighter Archetype ~ Unarmed Fighter],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.FighterWeaponProficiencies,TYPE.FighterArmorProficiencies,TYPE.FighterBonusFeats,TYPE.FighterBravery,TYPE.FighterWeaponTraining_ALL,TYPE.FighterArmorTraining_ALL,TYPE.FighterArmorMastery,TYPE.FighterWeaponMastery]								DESC:Not all fighters need weapons to make their mark on the world. The unarmed fighter picks up a weapon only rarely, and when he does, he prefers the weapons of the monk. There are even those who mistake them for monks, but these fighters enter the fight without ki, and instead have a tough perseverance that few can rival.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	AUTO:FEAT|Armor Proficiency (Light)|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1						ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Monk Weapon Proficiencies|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Improved Unarmed Strike|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Harsh Training ~ Unarmed Fighter|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=2	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Tough Guy ~ Unarmed Fighter|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Training ~ Unarmed Fighter|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=5	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Clever Wrestler ~ Unarmed Fighter|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=7	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Trick Throw ~ Unarmed Fighter|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=9	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Takedown ~ Una