ARCANE BOMBER		KEY:Wizard Archetype ~ ARCANE BOMBER	CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.WizardArchetype.WizardArcaneBond.WizardArcaneSchool	PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Wizard Archetype ~ ARCANE BOMBER],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.WizardArcaneBond,TYPE.WizardArcaneSchool]	DESC:To many wizards, the experimentation of the alchemist seems quaint, if not dangerous or frightening. A few wizards take up the secrets of the bomb, however, fusing alchemy with their already considerable magical power.																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.74	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Bomb ~ ARCANE BOMBER|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Spellblast Bombs ~ ARCANE BOMBER|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|School of the Bomb ~ ARCANE BOMBER|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1
